title: Laptop
description:
Written by Kerry O'Brien
Starring: Jonathan Marballi, Alene Latimer, Lisa Kleinman, Langan Kingsley, Kelly Hudson, Avery Monsen, Zack Phillips, Kristy Lopez-Bernal, Dan Hodapp, James McCarthy, Jon Bershad

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, May 8, 2013.

Filmed by Tom Levin, Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
